273
00:25:56,624 --> 00:25:59,536
Just go over to her
and say hello.

274
00:26:01,385 --> 00:26:03,341
Everything will be fine.

275
00:26:05,785 --> 00:26:07,298
Trust me.

276
00:26:11,986 --> 00:26:14,216
I will do that.

277
00:26:23,388 --> 00:26:26,663
Hi... I'm sorry, I don't normally do this, but...
- I'm a Virgo...

278
00:26:26,828 --> 00:26:30,980
and before you ask,
no, I don't come here often.

279
00:26:36,508 --> 00:26:39,070
