312
00:28:46,603 --> 00:28:48,162
Of course you do.

313
00:28:52,604 --> 00:28:55,614
I hope you're better at cards
than you are at air hockey.

314
00:28:55,615 --> 00:28:56,393
- You know what?

315
00:28:57,724 --> 00:29:00,319
This time I'm gonna win.
- Let's go.

316
00:29:03,605 --> 00:29:05,163
Oh my god, are you OK?

317
00:29:05,164 --> 00:29:06,206
Yeah.

318
00:29:12,806 --> 00:29:15,002
What if I'm not?

319
00:29:15,601 --> 00:29:19,150
Well I...

320
00:29:27,968 --> 00:29:31,597
I'm fine.
- The bounce.

321
00:29:31,768 --> 00:29:33,281
The bounce.

322
00:29:41,649 --> 00:29:43,527
Good trip, huh?

323
00:29:44,249 --> 00:29:46,001
Definitely.

324
00:29:50,090 --> 00:29:53,400
You like that girl?
You have a good time last night?

325
00:29:54,770 --> 00:29:57,126
And this morning.

