329
00:30:14,373 --> 00:30:16,887
To hear me.

330
00:30:17,053 --> 00:30:21,969
Friday night there's a tournament
in New Orleans.

331
00:30:23,814 --> 00:30:27,363
Next Friday?
- Yes. Is that a problem?

332
00:30:27,534 --> 00:30:30,493
No, not a problem.

333
00:30:30,655 --> 00:30:33,539
Hey Dad, a friend of mine
wants to go to Santa Barbara,

334
00:30:33,540 --> 00:30:35,445
I was wondering if I could take a day?

335
00:30:35,615 --> 00:30:38,767
I know, I know.  This is the last time.
I swear.

336
00:30:39,095 --> 00:30:40,814
Thanks. Bye.

337
00:30:40,975 --> 00:30:44,127
Bad news, baby,
I gotta to Cleveland.

338
00:30:44,296 --> 00:30:47,891
I should be back by Monday.
I'll call you later this evening.

339
00:31:29,581 --> 00:31:33,779
Well done. We are going to rest.
Tomorrow is a big day.

340
00:31:33,942 --> 00:31:39,016
Rest? I've won.
Let us go a little drink, or something.

341
00:31:42,583 --> 00:31:44,460
So far so good.

342
00:31:45,583 --> 00:31:47,778
That's all you got to say?

343
00:31:49,424 --> 00:31:52,017
Just calm down.

344
00:31:52,184 --> 00:31:55,971
Maybe you'll feel better tomorrow
when I win $600,000.

345
00:32:16,586 --> 00:32:18,976
What about Helen!

346
00:32:19,147 --> 00:32:21,707
Do not answer the phone.

347
00:32:21,867 --> 00:32:24,859
Why?
- Because...

348
00:32:26,347 --> 00:32:30,057
Your opponents tomorrow
want to keep you up

349
00:32:30,228 --> 00:32:31,564
Maybe it's important.

350
00:32:31,565 --> 00:32:35,063
- Don't open the door,
I'm telling you for your own good.

351
00:32:35,228 --> 00:32:36,980
What if it's important.

352
00:32:38,348 --> 00:32:41,420
Hi, I'm Shaniqua
and this is my friend Alley.

353
00:32:46,149 --> 00:32:47,821
I told you.

354
00:32:57,391 --> 00:33:00,781
You can can beat everyone at this table,
with or without sleep.

355
00:33:49,237 --> 00:33:52,228
Rough cards.
- False.

356
00:33:52,396 --> 00:33:55,230
You know it's not the cards
and so do I.

357
00:33:55,397 --> 00:33:57,513
There isn't anything I could do.

358
00:33:58,997 --> 00:34:01,386
You're tired.

359
00:34:01,557 --> 00:34:04,072
You're right back to your old bad habits.

360
00:34:04,237 --> 00:34:06,911
You're in love with your money.

361
00:34:07,078 --> 00:34:10,468
I can tell what everyone has.
