363
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:18,753
You call lying to your wife a promise?

364
00:34:27,640 --> 00:34:30,109
You'd better go home.

365
00:34:45,322 --> 00:34:47,392
What's going on, Honey?

366
00:34:47,915 --> 00:34:48,958
What?

367
00:34:50,963 --> 00:34:52,555
Where were you, in Las Vegas?

368
00:34:56,084 --> 00:34:58,555
Well, went to New Orleans.
-New Orleans?

369
00:34:58,556 --> 00:35:00,953
Yeah, for a tournament.
- I knew it.

370
00:35:01,124 --> 00:35:04,913
I'm not playing any cards at all.
I'm just teaching a kid...

371
00:35:05,085 --> 00:35:09,601
How much did you lose?
-$10,000.

372
00:35:09,765 --> 00:35:12,160
$10,000?
-Yeah.

373
00:35:12,161 --> 00:35:14,555
Tommy.
- But in Vegas...

374
00:35:14,725 --> 00:35:17,604
When were you in Vegas?

375
00:35:19,087 --> 00:35:21,602
I want you to understand though,
we were in Vegas...

376
00:35:21,603 --> 00:35:22,999
- I'm goin' to my sisters.

377
00:35:32,448 --> 00:35:36,487
Hi, Michelle, it's me.
Can you call me back?

378
00:35:38,608 --> 00:35:43,046
Three messages, and she won't call me back.
- Will you stop worrying about her.

379
00:35:43,209 --> 00:35:46,963
Let's think of winning.
- What's first place, anyway?

380
00:35:47,129 --> 00:35:49,324
$500,000.

381
00:36:06,371 --> 00:36:09,444
Guess who?
- How many guesses do I get?

382
00:36:09,612 --> 00:36:13,651
One. Did you have fun the other night?
- Oh my god, you're here.

383
00:36:13,812 --> 00:36:18,967
How's it going so far?
- Really good, but it just got a whole lot better.

384
00:36:24,174 --> 00:36:26,563
It's nice to see you again.

385
00:36:28,374 --> 00:36:30,729
Yeah, you too.

386
00:36:30,894 --> 00:36:33,124
Do you want some?
- No, thanks.

387
00:36:41,536 --> 00:36:43,049
What?

388
00:36:43,216 --> 00:36:45,012
Nothing.

389
00:36:45,815 --> 00:36:48,010
There's just something about you.

390
00:37:01,497 --> 00:37:03,374
You're a nice guy.

391
00:37:21,700 --> 00:37:23,736
Is there something wrong?

392
00:37:27,100 --> 00:37:29,660
I wish...
- What?

393
00:37:32,181 --> 00:37:35,969
I wish I'd met you under
different circumstances.

394
00:37:37,462 --> 00:37:39,293
