401
00:38:33,708 --> 00:38:36,427
And I need to rest.
- You can sleep here.

402
00:38:58,390 --> 00:39:00,460
I'll call you later, okay?

403
00:39:06,991 --> 00:39:08,982
Good luck tomorrow.

404
00:39:14,752 --> 00:39:18,029
Is she there?
- Yeah, I'll call her, hold on.

405
00:39:25,633 --> 00:39:27,589
How's it going?

406
00:39:28,874 --> 00:39:32,389
Where are you?
- I'm in...

407
00:39:33,514 --> 00:39:36,666
I'm in Vegas with that kid,
Alex.

408
00:39:38,075 --> 00:39:40,953
The World Poker Tour Championship.

409
00:39:41,114 --> 00:39:42,721
It starts in about two weeks.

410
00:39:42,722 --> 00:39:45,826
I need to get him in shape
and then get him out of here.

411
00:39:47,595 --> 00:39:52,829
Listen, this is it.
If it's over, then it's all over.

412
00:39:52,996 --> 00:39:55,874
I never thought we'd have
this conversation again.

413
00:39:56,036 --> 00:40:01,556
Listen, we got our money back,
all the money, a lot and some interest.

414
00:40:01,717 --> 00:40:02,826
That's not the point.

415
00:40:02,827 --> 00:40:05,677
- What do you mean it's not
the point, it is the point.

416
00:40:05,837 --> 00:40:07,556
Goodbye, Tommy.

417
00:41:27,607 --> 00:41:30,201
Sorry about those last few hands.
- You'll do fine.

418
00:41:30,367 --> 00:41:33,724
And we made some money.
- And what we have earned.

419
00:41:34,127 --> 00:41:36,516
A little money, come on.
60 grand each.

420
00:41:38,568 --> 00:41:40,923
Well, minus expenses.

421
00:41:42,008 --> 00:41:43,919
Bellagio.
Bellagio.

422
00:41:50,210 --> 00:41:51,847
Hold on.

423
00:41:53,933 --> 00:41:54,976
Michelle.
Michelle.

424
00:41:58,106 --> 00:41:59,149
Hey.
- Hi.

425
00:42:02,931 --> 00:42:07,129
Is this your dad?
- Yeah, I'm her daddy.

426
00:42:07,291 --> 00:42:09,759
At least for tonight.

427
00:42:09,931 --> 00:42:11,808
Wait. What?

428
00:42:15,572 --> 00:42:17,961
Go find you own girl.

429
00:42:24,093 --> 00:42:26,448
Do you feel bad for me or something?

430
00:42:28,333 --> 00:42:32,566
Look, you don't understand that at this point...
- Did anyone pay you?

431
00:42:50,736 --> 00:42:52,647
It's Tommy.

432
00:42:54,216 --> 00:42:58,927
