It was a dumb idea.

433
00:43:07,270 --> 00:43:08,313
Hello.

434
00:43:26,563 --> 00:43:27,606
Hello.

435
00:43:27,938 --> 00:43:29,496
Hi, what are you doing?

436
00:43:30,018 --> 00:43:34,218
Listen to me, I know this seems
like a hell of a lot of money.

437
00:43:35,060 --> 00:43:40,897
When you think about it,
it's nothing compared to what we could do.

438
00:43:41,742 --> 00:43:45,212
