442
00:43:59,823 --> 00:44:02,337
Helping people is more than that.

443
00:44:09,544 --> 00:44:11,900
Yeah...
Maybe you're right.

444
00:44:16,225 --> 00:44:18,102
I'm home.

445
00:44:23,066 --> 00:44:26,183
Jordy, let us alone.
- Just one more second.

446
00:44:26,184 --> 00:44:27,227
Jordan.

447
00:44:32,546 --> 00:44:34,618
I'll hear everything.

448
00:44:38,067 --> 00:44:42,539
