450
00:44:55,989 --> 00:45:00,745
Alex, I didn't spend the last 20 years
of my life working my ass off

451
00:45:00,910 --> 00:45:05,268
so you could play cards for a living!
- I had a partial scholarship.

452
00:45:05,431 --> 00:45:08,980
