be an amazing week for poker.

468
00:47:24,166 --> 00:47:27,522
Mike, we have five
exciting days of poker ahead of us.

469
00:47:27,686 --> 00:47:29,952
Each player has to put up a $25,000 each

470
00:47:29,953 --> 00:47:33,124
